title: Sen. Blackburn hits back at criticism from California Dem: Tennesseeans will reopen in 'smart, strategic way'
description: Tennessee residents will go about reopening their state in a "smart strategic way" with coronavirus precautions, Sen. Marsha Blackburn promised Tuesday evening.
